  "cursorSync": "Crosshair",
  "description": "Weekly real EC2 cost (CloudWatch EstimatedCharges, ServiceName=AmazonEC2), meta-fleet CI hours for pytorch/pytorch, and EC2 cost per CI-hour.",
  "editable": true,
